      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 6, 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          sunkissed ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website sunkissed.band and related social media integrations. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> When you subscribe to our newsletter, contact us, or interact with our social media accounts, you may provide your name, email address, or other contact information.</li>
          <li><strong>Automatically collected information:</strong> When you visit our website, we may collect basic usage data such as pages visited, browser type, and referring URL through standard web analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Social media data:</strong> If you interact with us through Instagram or other social media platforms, we may receive your public profile information and messages you send to us.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Send you updates about new music, shows, and band news (if you subscribed)</li>
          <li>Respond to your messages and inquiries</li>
          <li>Improve our website and online presence</li>
          <li>Communicate with fans through social media</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with service providers who help us operate our website and social media (e.g., Netlify for hosting, Meta for Instagram integration), but only as necessary to provide those services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. You can request deletion of your data at any time (see below).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Unsubscribe from our communications at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, please visit our <a href="/data-deletion">Data Deletion page</a> or contact us at <a href="mailto:sunkissed.hills@gmail.com">sunkissed.hills@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          Our website and integrations may use third-party services including Meta (Instagram), Spotify, Apple Music, and others. These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:sunkissed.hills@gmail.com">sunkissed.hills@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
